de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.utilities.datastructures.arrays

Class DoubleIntegerArrayQuickSort

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.utilities.datastructures.arrays.DoubleIntegerArrayQuickSort

  • public class DoubleIntegerArrayQuickSort
extends Object
    Class to sort a double and an integer DBID array, using a quicksort with a best of 5 heuristic.
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
